01:46.066 --> 01:47.133 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
No action taken.

01:47.133 --> 01:49.233 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Nothing.

01:49.233 --> 01:53.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
