17:29.066 --> 17:33.400 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We begin in the southern
city of Krasnodar.

17:33.400 --> 17:38.400 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: It is
Sunday morning in Russia's
conservative south.

17:41.300 --> 17:44.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
