Christian is the only
way to be a true Russian.

17:59.866 --> 18:03.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
FATHER JOHN, Archpriest
(through translator): The
state and my faith are united.

18:03.333 --> 18:04.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
