and the state coincide.

18:08.333 --> 18:12.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: In Russia,
faith is patriotic.

18:12.900 --> 18:17.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Orthodox Church criticizes
liberal Western values as
heresies, while Orthodox priests

18:17.700 --> 18:21.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
