and endorse Putin
politically and personally.

18:21.033 --> 18:23.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The president's faith
increases his popularity.

18:23.800 --> 18:27.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
FATHER JOHN (through
translator): He is a
religious man, and he
takes part in the divine

18:27.900 --> 18:29.933 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
