people in churches.

18:29.933 --> 18:34.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What the president is doing,
what the government is doing, of
course, we support it, because

18:34.666 --> 18:37.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
