and truthfully.

18:37.166 --> 18:42.066 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Today's
reenergized Orthodox
Church helps create pride
in a shared religion.

18:44.600 --> 18:49.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
