is in its traditions.

19:26.900 --> 19:31.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: For 17
years, Vladimir Gromov led
the regional Cossack army.

19:31.833 --> 19:36.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
