the Order of Friendship Medal.

19:40.766 --> 19:45.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Gromov considers Putin the
custodian of Russian pride and
stability, preventing the chaos

19:46.433 --> 19:48.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
